MeasurementToolMetadata.Description: Magnetic Resonance Spectroscopy analysis statistics calculated from the HERCULES acquisition.
MeasurementToolMetadata.Name: Osprey HERCULES diff2 AlphaCorrWaterScaled

age.name: img_osprey_HERCULES_diff2_AlphaCorrWaterScaled_Voxel_1_Basis_1_age
age.Description: Age (in years) of the candidate at the time of the first acquired scan

gestational_age.name: img_osprey_HERCULES_diff2_AlphaCorrWaterScaled_Voxel_1_Basis_1_gestational_age
gestational_age.Description: Gestational age (in days) based on the EDD

GABA.name: img_osprey_HERCULES_diff2_AlphaCorrWaterScaled_Voxel_1_Basis_1_GABA
GABA.Description: GABA alpha-corrected molal concentration, using tissue corrected water
GABA.note: GABA scaled to tissue corrected water according to Gasparovic et al, Magn Reson Med 55:1219-26 (2006). Alpha (cWM/cGM) correction applied according to: ConcIU/(fGM + alpha*fWM), with group normalization: (meanfGM + alpha * meanfWM) / ((fGM + alpha * fWM) * (meanfGM + meanfWM))
